$ SQL Server: reconfigure
@ reconfigure

The `reconfigure` or `reconfigure with override` statements are required after changing a *server property* with → development/databases/SQL-Server/administration/schemas/sys/objects/stored-procedures/sp_configure[`sp_configure`].

`reconfigure` executes within a → development/databases/SQL-Server/architecture/transaction: either all or none of the reconfiguration opteraions take effect.

sa:

  → development/databases/SQL-Server/T-SQL/statements[T-SQL statements]
